name: Styx Canyon (South Fork)
description:
Introduction

Approach

The approach for South Fire starts at Dante's Peak and drops into the top of Coffin Canyon. There are some nice down climbs and one rappel here. When you enter a larger wash/meadow you will cross dcr over a bit of rocks and down into Styx. During the superblooms, this meadow holds an incredible amount of perfumed flowers.
